{
  "page": "Anguy",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\"><img alt=\"Brotherhood without banners.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/50px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/75px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/100px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Anguy<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Archer</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\"><img alt=\"Brotherhood without banners.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/50px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/75px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/100px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Lucas_Soriana_Anguy_the_Archer.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Lucas Soriana Anguy the Archer.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Lucas_Soriana_Anguy_the_Archer.jpg/250px-Lucas_Soriana_Anguy_the_Archer.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Lucas_Soriana_Anguy_the_Archer.jpg/375px-Lucas_Soriana_Anguy_the_Archer.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Lucas_Soriana_Anguy_the_Archer.jpg/500px-Lucas_Soriana_Anguy_the_Archer.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Anguy the Archer, by Lucas Soriana © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Aliases</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Archer<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li>Anguy the Archer<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">Brotherhood without banners</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Marcher</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Dornish Marches</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafanguy.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafanguy.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_McGinley\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Philip McGinley\">Philip McGinley</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_3\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 3\">Season 3</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Anguy</b>, called the <b>Anguy the Archer</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> or simply <b>Archer</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">commoner</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Dornish Marches</a> who is skilled with the bow.\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, Anguy is portrayed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_McGinley\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Philip McGinley\">Philip McGinley</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Anguy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Anguy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Anguy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Anguy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Anguy\" title=\"Category:Images of Anguy\">Images of Anguy</a></div>\n<p>Anguy is skinny with freckles and red hair. He is fairly young.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Anguy carries a longbow<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> and uses arrows tipped with bodkins as well as broadheads.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> He is highly valued due to his exceptional skill with a bow.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> The only songs he knows are <a href=\"/index.php/Marcher_ballads\" title=\"Marcher ballads\">marcher ballads</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Fern\" title=\"Fern\">Fern</a>, a girl at <a href=\"/index.php/Lambswold\" title=\"Lambswold\">Lambswold</a>, fancies Anguy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand%27s_tourney\" title=\"Hand&#39;s tourney\">Hand's tourney</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> in celebration of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>'s ascension as <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, Anguy wins the archery competition, outshooting Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Swann\" title=\"Balon Swann\">Balon Swann</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jalabhar_Xho\" title=\"Jalabhar Xho\">Jalabhar Xho</a> at a hundred paces and earning himself a sum of ten thousand <a href=\"/index.php/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">golden dragons</a>. He refuses an offer from Eddard to join the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark_guards\" title=\"House Stark guards\">Hand's guard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Having spent and lost his fortune, Anguy joins Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a> when Eddard dispatches him to bring Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Laws_and_justice_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Laws and justice of the Seven Kingdoms\">justice</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafanguy.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafanguy.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Anguy is with the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">brotherhood without banners</a> party that captures <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Hot_Pie\" title=\"Hot Pie\">Hot Pie</a>. He shoots a duck which the outlaws give to <a href=\"/index.php/Sharna\" title=\"Sharna\">Sharna</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and then a <a href=\"/index.php/Goose\" title=\"Goose\">goose</a> as they continue their travels.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> Arya, who is unable to draw Anguy's longbow, is told tales of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Dornish Marches</a> by the archer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> He offers to make a light bow for her once they get to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> Anguy uses his arrows to put <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> starving in <a href=\"/index.php/Crow_cage\" title=\"Crow cage\">crow cages</a> out of their misery at <a href=\"/index.php/Stoney_Sept\" title=\"Stoney Sept\">Stoney Sept</a>, and he flirts with a freckle-faced wench at the <a href=\"/index.php/Peach\" title=\"Peach\">Peach</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The outlaws bring the three captured youths to Beric in the <a href=\"/index.php/Hollow_hill\" title=\"Hollow hill\">hollow hill</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Like most members of the brotherhood, Anguy is now a follower of <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Anguy takes part in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_burning_septry\" title=\"Battle at the burning septry\">battle at the burning septry</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a>, shooting several of the sellswords.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> He reveals he squandered his fortune at <a href=\"/index.php/Chataya%27s_brothel\" title=\"Chataya&#39;s brothel\">Chataya's brothel</a>, enjoying lavish excesses with <a href=\"/index.php/Jayde\" title=\"Jayde\">Jayde</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alayaya\" title=\"Alayaya\">Alayaya</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Dancy\" title=\"Dancy\">Dancy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> Beric orders Anguy to aid in keeping watch for <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> Arya helps Anguy dry horses at the ruins of a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrook\" title=\"House Goodbrook\">Goodbrook</a> village.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After Beric's final death,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> a part of the brotherhood, including Anguy, go their separate way from those who chose to follow the resurrected, vengeful <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Stoneheart\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady Stoneheart\">Lady Stoneheart</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafanguy.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafanguy.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Anguy\">Quotes by Anguy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Anguy\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Arya</b>: You missed.<br />\n<b>Anguy</b>: More fool you if you think so. They go where I send them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> and Anguy</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tom</b>: I'd dearly love someone to sing with, that I would. <a href=\"/index.php/Lem\" title=\"Lem\">Lem</a> can't carry a tune, and our longbow lad only knows <a href=\"/index.php/Marcher\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Marcher\">marcher</a> ballads, every one of them a hundred verses long.<br />\n<b>Anguy</b>: We sing real songs in the marches.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom of Sevenstreams</a> and Anguy</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>When I don't fancy a man's eyes, I put an arrow through one.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Anguy to <a href=\"/index.php/Husband\" title=\"Husband\">Husband</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Sandor</b>: You didn't leave me enough <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> to buy a cup of <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a>, you whoresons.<br />\n</p><p><b>Anguy</b>: We're <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaws\" title=\"Outlaws\">outlaws</a>. Outlaws steal. It's in the songs, if you ask nice <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom</a> may sing you one. Be thankful we didn't kill you.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Sandor</b>: Come try it, Archer. I'll take that quiver off you and shove those arrows up your freckly little arse.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> and Anguy</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Lem</b>: How'd <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">that bloody bastard</a> get all that <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> anyhow?<br />\n</p><p><b>Anguy</b>: He won the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand%27s_tourney\" title=\"Hand&#39;s tourney\">Hand's tourney</a>. In <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. I won a fair fortune myself, but then I met <a href=\"/index.php/Dancy\" title=\"Dancy\">Dancy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jayde\" title=\"Jayde\">Jayde</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Alayaya\" title=\"Alayaya\">Alayaya</a>. They taught me what roast <a href=\"/index.php/Swan\" title=\"Swan\">swan</a> tastes like, and how to bathe in <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a>.<br />\n<b>Harwin</b>: Pissed it all away, did you?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Anguy</b>: Not all. I bought these boots, and this excellent dagger.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Lem\" title=\"Lem\">Lem</a>, Anguy, and <a href=\"/index.php/Harwin\" title=\"Harwin\">Harwin</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Anguy\">Quotes about Anguy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Anguy\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>That afternoon a boy named Anguy, an unheralded commoner from the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Dornish Marches</a>, won the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand%27s_tourney\" title=\"Hand&#39;s tourney\">archery competition</a>, outshooting Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Swann\" title=\"Balon Swann\">Balon Swann</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jalabhar_Xho\" title=\"Jalabhar Xho\">Jalabhar Xho</a> at a hundred paces after all the other bowmen had been eliminated at the shorter distances. Ned sent <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn\" title=\"Alyn\">Alyn</a> to seek him out and offer him a position with the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark_guards\" title=\"House Stark guards\">Hand's guard</a>, but the boy was flush with <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> and victory and riches undreamed of, and he refused.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tom</b>: Boy, put up that sword now, unless you're wanting to be hurt. It's too big for you, lad, and besides, Anguy here could put three shafts through you before you could hope to reach us.<br />\n<b>Arya</b>: He could not, and I'm a girl.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom of Sevenstreams</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The archer's hand moved quicker than Arya would have believed. His shaft went hissing past her head within an inch of her ear and buried itself in the trunk of the willow behind her. By then the bowman had a second arrow notched and drawn. She'd thought she understood what <a href=\"/index.php/Syrio_Forel\" title=\"Syrio Forel\">Syrio</a> meant by quick as a s<a href=\"/index.php?title=Nake&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nake (page does not exist)\">nake</a> and smooth as summer silk, but now she knew she hadn't.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> was probably inspired by his father when he wrote about Anguy spending ten thousand golden dragons on women and drinking as his father won ten thousand dollars by gambling during World War II. He had a good time with the money, spending it all on women, beer, nightclubs, and the track.<sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gameofthrones.fandom.com/wiki/Anguy\">Anguy</a> on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gameofthrones.fandom.com/wiki/Wiki_of_Westeros\">Wiki of Westeros</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Anguy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ras